{
  "texts": [
    "In some places, same-sex couples now have the ability to get married, adopt children, and take advantage of healthcare benefits, all of which were previously unavailable to them.",
    "Additionally, I know many people who believe that being gay is a personal choice and who still value the rights and beliefs of LGBTQ+ individuals.",
    "We can all coexist with respect, regardless of our opinions.",
    "one-shotI disagree that being gay should have the same rights as everyone else.",
    "Everyone should be treated fairly and with respect, but I do not believe that our rights are identical."
  ]
}